seq.a: The party sends a warrant possession request asking a warrant to be released
The Client Service Back Office as part of the Small Claims Registry Operations receives the request and retrieves the SCTT file
the SCT Warrant Possession is forwarded to Queensland Police
The SCTT physical file is stored by the Back Office awaiting a report to be sent by the Police
the respective SCT file is retrieved
Back Office attaches the new SCT document, and stores the expanded SCT physical file
some other MC internal staff receives the physical SCT file (out of scope)
